<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1874,2007]" pageId="3" pageNumber="52">
This species was described in 
<taxonomicName authority="Chapuis, 1879" authorityName="Chapuis" authorityYear="1879" box="[486,736,1874,1899]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Ergana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[486,569,1875,1898]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="52">Ergana</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Chapuis" box="[575,736,1874,1899]" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" refString="Chapuis, F. (1879) Phytophages Abyssiniens du Musee Civique d'Histoire Naturelle de Genes. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova, 15, 15 - 31." type="journal article" year="1879">
Chapuis, 
<number box="[680,736,1875,1899]" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" value="1879.0">1879</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and Laboissière transferred it to 
<taxonomicName box="[1102,1224,1875,1899]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Pimentelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1102,1224,1875,1899]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="52">Pimentelia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the paper where this genus was originally described (
<bibRefCitation author="Laboissiere" box="[561,760,1910,1935]" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" refString="Laboissiere, V. (1939) Galerucinae (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae) recueillis dans L'Angola par le Dr Monard. Archos Mus. Bocage, 10, 87 - 167." type="journal article" year="1939">
Laboissière 
<number box="[700,760,1911,1935]" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" value="1939.0">1939</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). Allocation to a genus is somewhat difficult, since the only available specimen from 
<collectingCountry box="[439,521,1946,1971]" name="Angola" pageId="3" pageNumber="52">Angola</collectingCountry>
is a female. External characters show that it is not closely related to 
<taxonomicName box="[1315,1436,1947,1971]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Pimentelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1315,1436,1947,1971]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="52">Pimentelia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and do not belong to this genus.
</paragraph>
